{"type": "article", "id": 7056, "title": "Day & Night 台灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-03-04T07:17:39Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 23, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234258JQTn8ezCRldMUcAP.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\tÉleÌonore Delisse 是 荷兰 Eindhoven 设计学院的一名学生，这款灯是 ÉleÌonore Delisse 的毕业作品。在世界范围内，季节性情绪失调（Seasonal Affective Disorder，SAD）是困扰许多人的问题，\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\tÉleÌonore Delisse 希望通过这个作品来缓解人们的“冬季忧郁症”。玻璃在不同的广源下会呈现不同的颜色——白天冷色调来刺激头脑的清醒，夜晚的暖色光有助于睡眠。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234257xZapF9lUctJfEwAq.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;\" data-ratio=\"1.33521924\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n\t</p>\r\n\t<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234257xCUTYfIl01udejcw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.944\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n\t</p>\r\n\t<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234258BcLw75MuG2qj0HWY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59351852\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n\t</p>\r\n\t<div>\r\n\t\t<br>\r\n\t</div>\r\n\n\n"}